<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About CodeSphere</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #1f1f1f;
            padding: 1rem 5%;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .navbar h1 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #4c8bf5;
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: #4c8bf5;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }
        .navbar a:hover {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 3rem auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #4c8bf5;
        }
        .features, .advantages {
            margin: 2rem 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        ul li {
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        ul li::before {
            content: '\2713';
            color: #4c8bf5;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .cta {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .cta button {
            background-color: #4c8bf5;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta button:hover {
            background-color: #357ae8;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <h1>CodeSphere</h1>
        <div>
            <a href="/index">Register</a>
            <a href="/login">Login</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>About CodeSphere</h2>
        <p>CodeSphere is an interactive learning platform designed to help you master data structures and algorithms (DSA) and enhance your coding skills. Our user-friendly interface, comprehensive exercises, and built-in coding IDE provide the perfect environment for learning.</p>
        <div class="features">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Supports multiple programming languages</li>
                <li>Interactive problem-solving environment</li>
                <li>Detailed progress tracking</li>
                <li>Step-by-step DSA guidance</li>
                <li>Built-in coding IDE for hands-on practice</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="advantages">
            <h2>Why Choose CodeSphere?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Improve coding proficiency with targeted exercises</li>
                <li>Access up-to-date learning resources</li>
                <li>Prepare effectively for technical interviews</li>
                <li>Track your learning progress in real-time</li>
                <li>Join a community of passionate developers</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="cta">
            <p>Start your journey with CodeSphere today and become a proficient developer.</p>
            <button onclick="location.href='/index'">Join CodeSphere Now</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
